    <step order="3">Create useOfficeTheme hook to detect and respond to theme changes</step>
    <step order="4">Create TaskPaneShell component with header and content areas</step>
    <step order="5">Create basic routing structure (Save view, Share view, Status view)</step>
    <step order="6">Create placeholder components for each main view</step>
    <step order="7">Set up CSS-in-JS with makeStyles from Fluent UI v9</step>
    <step order="8">Add theme tokens usage examples in shell component</step>
    <step order="9">Create taskpane.html host page with Office.js script reference</step>
    <step order="10">Update webpack to output to dist/taskpane/</step>
    <step order="11">Verify build succeeds and app renders in browser</step>
    <step order="12">Update TASK-INDEX.md: change this task's status to âœ… completed</step>
