    </test>
  </ui-tests>

  <notes>
    Office.js must be initialized before the React app renders. Use the Office.onReady()
    callback to ensure proper initialization sequence. The theme detection should use
    Office.context.ui.roamingSettings if available, with fallback to system preference.
  </notes>

